【冰魄寒刀】(bingpo-blade)
学习要求：max_neili>=100，huagong-dafa>=125，sanyin-wugongzhao>=120
	chousui-zhang>=120，tianshan-zhang>=120，zhaixinggong>=120，chanhun-suo>=120
	xuantian-strike>=120
